<HEAD>Californian Wins `Lady Universe' Contest</HEAD>
<DATELINE>MADONNA DI CAMPIGLIO, Italy (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   A 28-year-old Californian was
selected as Lady Universe 1989 from a group of 28 women, organizers
announced Friday.
   Blond, blue-eyed Julia Jones of San Francisco was crowned at a
ceremony Thursday night in this small Italian town just south of the
